<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p>Intermediate events happen during the course of a process. Forms supports one kind of intermediate event, a timer event.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Timer intermediate events used within the main process flow delay the flow.</li>
            <li>Timer intermediate events attached to user tasks are used for exception handling and cause an exception flow to be taken.</li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>